I got mine here:

http://www.mtmfg.com

They carry the West Coast Metric seals but, unlike WCM, they had the vent
wing seals too for my 74 transporter. They also did not charge tax. I've
had a terrible time finding a reasonable installer. I can't do it myself
because my right arm is injured and I won't be able to do anything for
awhile. So far, I've taken it to three auto glass people and they know
nothing about it. Best estimate is $900.00 labor from a "restoration" shop.
People like to screw you when you own a bus. I've gotten no help at all
from any shop. I would never do this again so good luck to you.


